# Pokémon Info Fetcher
A simple web app that fetches Pokémon details using the PokeAPI. Enter a name (like "pikachu") or get a random Pokémon.

**Live Demo**: [https://ashish-bose.github.io/pokemon-fetcher/]
**Features**: Displays name, image, height, weight, abilities.
**Tech**: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, PokeAPI.
